<plot>What is easier in these stressful times than to be able to combine two activities at the same time? The papal cab is one of those super solutions. The cab brings you where you want and at the same time you can do a confession with Father Mehrin. Richard has a problem with his wife. He doesn't like her tuna casseroles. It must be a sin, he thinks. Father Mehrin tries to help, but is too busy with the traffic around him or the traffic is too busy with him. Is there still time enough to teach Richard a valuable lesson?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?422405</url></doc>
